data.text: We have curated a special feature on South America's opulent property market, showcasing the most exquisite homes in Argentina, Brazil, Chile, and Paraguay. We also take you on a tour of the UK's stunning seaside properties that will leave you spellbound. Moreover, we're thrilled to feature Hawazen Esber, CEO of Development at Majid Al Futtaim Group, in Dubai, where we also cover the city's most luxurious properties, developments, and interiors. Our article on St John's Wood in London is sure to interest those keen on the property market. And we've added features on luxury concept superyachts, watches, and an article called "Worldwide Wellness," where you'll find the most luxurious hotels, resorts, and villas for a rejuvenating experience.
